text: Pascual Beká Elebiyó Eyang (born 17 August 1999), known as Pascual and Nasty, is an Equatoguinean footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Liga Nacional de Fútbol club Cano Sport Academy and the Equatorial Guinea national team. ==International career== Pascual made his international debut for Equatorial Guinea in 2018. ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:Equatoguinean footballers Category:People from Ebebiyín Category:Equatorial Guinea international footballers Category:Cano Sport Academy players
